          <p class="big-paragraph">SciVisColor is the brainchild of Francesca Samsel, professional
            artist-turned-visualization specialist. SciVisColor is a one-stop-shop for hundreds of
            custom linear, divergent, convergent, “wave,” and discrete colormaps, color sets, color
            guidance, examples of artist-driven color usage in a wide variety of scientific
            visualizations, and Colormoves—a user-friendly colormap creation and low-stakes
            data exploration tool.</p>
